g.title: j2852080779
g.text: So, I never got the whole story of how you met Arthur.

g.title: j3557267841
g.text: Do you have a second to chat, Lettie? Or are you busy?

g.title: j1034265276
g.text: Figured you didn't want the gory details
But, sí, if you want to know

g.title: j1863501612
g.text: We were stationed together in the same base
Him in the Britannic and me with the Libertatian Army

g.title: j282741027
g.text: But I can take a break

g.title: j2257786747
g.text: I was the field medic for my regiment
We were deployed in next to his

g.title: j2074499064
g.text: I was wondering how you and Arthur met.

g.title: j815293593
g.text: Most of my crew didn't make it
I stitched his arm up good jaja
When he retired and went into the ICR
I was sick of all the drama that goes on in the army anyway

g.title: j592813331
g.text: I told him I'd follow him to the ends of the earth
Didn't realize I'd follow him to the edge of Mictlán

g.title: j1891339950
g.text: It must seem so small to you
You have danced with La Flaca so many times

g.title: j1559415135
g.text: Just because my fights are a bit spectacular doesn't mean I can't appreciate how horrible it must've been.

g.title: j4057956207
g.text: All war is shit, end of story.

g.title: j1198611085
g.text: Bright and flashy or small and personal
La Flaca is all the same in the end

g.title: j2143443315
g.text: No matter how big and stupid the guns
